{"tid":770527,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本遭水災拼膠模型店再開業 泡水模型一折銷售","createTime":"2018-08-07T07:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T08:22:41.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"84535389feaff804a9cdef01138d545fcbe51e82","tid":770527,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"之前我們報導過被稱為&ldquo;塑膠拼裝模型聖地&rdquo;的塑膠拼裝模型店&ldquo;エラヤ&rdquo;遭受水災，店內所有的模型都被泥水浸泡，損失超過1億日元。大家得知消息後也是紛紛鼓勵店家要堅持下去並且想要提供幫助，今天（8月6日），塑膠拼裝模型店&ldquo;エラヤ&rdquo;通過網絡宣布將再次開店，並且將以一折的價格出售受損的模型，想要淘寶的朋友們可不要錯過了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/08/20180806_lr_176_4/gamersky_01small_02_2018861446CC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F08%2F20180806_lr_176_4%2Fgamersky_01small_02_2018861446CC0.jpg&h=8076b39f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/08/20180806_lr_176_4/gamersky_02small_04_2018861446448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F08%2F20180806_lr_176_4%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2018861446448.jpg&h=e594e74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過長時間的整理後，&ldquo;エラヤ&rdquo;終於在今日起開放一般顧客購買遭大雨受損的模型商品，每件受損商品將以官網公告的1折價格售出，營業時間為日本時間9點- 13點。若各位玩具人有機會走過路過，就不要錯過難得的尋寶機會。店裡目前還是很多淤泥和大量的整理工作，若是正好過來淘寶，也順便幫幫店長吧。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/08/20180806_lr_176_4/gamersky_03small_06_2018861446AD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F08%2F20180806_lr_176_4%2Fgamersky_03small_06_2018861446AD0.jpg&h=c4825b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/08/20180806_lr_176_4/gamersky_04small_08_2018861446258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F08%2F20180806_lr_176_4%2Fgamersky_04small_08_2018861446258.jpg&h=93517c7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff4c9d6a3406a7018ed9234a204801600fa316b3","tid":77052